nodes.text: function_mint(addressto,uint256tokenId)internalvirtual{require(to!=address(0),"ERC721: mint to the zero address");require(!_exists(tokenId),"ERC721: token already minted");_beforeTokenTransfer(address(0),to,tokenId);_balances[to]+=1;_owners[tokenId]=to;emitTransfer(address(0),to,tokenId);}
